a.n: Red Hot Chili Peppers - Red Hot Chili Peppers: Bonnaroo Festival

p.d: Filmed at Great Stage Park, Manchester, Tennessee, this concert film will give all fans a spectacular Live experience from start to finish. Classic Red Hot Chili Peppers featuring unforgettable version of their hits: 'Califonication', 'Give It Away', 'Scar Tissue' and many more.
